<HEAD>___</HEAD>
<TEXT>
 As he campaigned in the area, <PERSON> Bush </PERSON> was repeatedly reminded by local reporters of a previous campaign visit here, when he went to a <LOCATION> Milwaukee </LOCATION> bowling alley _ and wound up sprawled on the lane. Questions like `` Plan to do any bowling this time?'' have abounded. `` You have a good memory,'' he told one inqusitor. `` I did fall down. But so did nine pins,'' he said in defense of his technique.
