before proposed truce to go into effect, Iran agreeing to truce,
Navy finds abandoned Iranian gunboat and seizes its arms. No pickup.
^By MONA ZIADE</NOTE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>NICOSIA, Cyprus (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
