 <PERSON> Robin </PERSON> <PERSON> Williams </PERSON> and his wife have decided to end their nine-year marriage, <PERSON> Williams </PERSON>' publicist said Thursday. <PERSON> Valerie </PERSON> <PERSON> Velardi </PERSON> <PERSON> Williams </PERSON>, 36, filed for a dissolution of the marriage from <ORGANIZATION> Williams </ORGANIZATION>, 35, publicist <PERSON> Mark </PERSON> <PERSON> Rutenberg </PERSON> said in a statement. `` Mr. and Mrs. <PERSON> Williams </PERSON> indicated that their relationship is amicable and that they continue to share parenting of their -LRB- 5-year-old -RRB- son, <PERSON> Zachary </PERSON>,'' the statement said. The publicist also said the couple will not discuss the matter in public. <PERSON> Williams </PERSON>, nominated for a best actor Academy Award for his performance as a manic Armed Forces radio disc jockey in `` Good Morning, <LOCATION> Vietnam </LOCATION>,'' lives with <PERSON> Marsha </PERSON> <PERSON> Garces </PERSON>, the former nanny for <PERSON> Zachary </PERSON>.
