peration in that area with the Chinese. `` We have not had a chance to talk that out, but it's possible our approaches could be synergistic,'' he said after the news conference. <PERSON> Searle </PERSON>, with headquarters in <LOCATION> Skokie </LOCATION><LOCATION> , </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Ill. </LOCATION>, develops, manufactures and markets prescription pharmaceuticals worldwide. It is a wholly owned subsidiary of <ORGANIZATION> Monsanto </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Co </ORGANIZATION>.
